CROWN
  Ten Levels In One - Defuse Scenario

Like your favorite ice-cream stacked high 
on a hot summers day, this level blends 
10 unique environments in a vertical
pancake to form one cohesive and digestible 
piece of deliciousness. Enjoy!
 
Counter-Terrorists: 
Defend the water plant(A), underground(B), 
and dock(C) from terrorists. Prevent the 
terrorists from planting the device and 
succeeding with their objective. 

Terrorists: 
Navigate your way up to the upper levels 
and destroy the objectives at the (C)docks, 
(B)underground, or (A)water plant. Always be 
aware of what's above you!
 
Other Notes: There are three objective sites
in this level. All grouped together and
labeled A, B, and C
